        <h2 class="title"><a href="/burning-man-2005-panoramas">Burning Man 2005 Panoramas</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Sun, 2006-07-16 23:48.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first taxonomy_term_86"><a href="/topic/burning-man" rel="tag" title="About burning man, my other home" class="taxonomy_term_86">Burning Man</a></li>
